{
     "title":{
        "translate": "djzc.dialog.elua.title",
        "fallback":"冬季战场 欢迎界面",
        "color":"yellow",
        "bold": true,
        "hover_event": {
            "action": "show_text",
            "value": {
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.author2",
                "fallback": "冬季战场制作组 编写"
            }
        }
     },
     "pause": false,
     "type":"multi_action",
     "body":[
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body1",
                "fallback":"欢迎来到冬季战场！加油，特种兵！",
                "color":"yellow"
            }
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body2",
                "fallback":"—— 源于《绝地求生：刺激战场》开局语音，也送给每一个走进60144的你。",
                "color":"white"
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body3",
                "fallback":"【健康游戏忠告】",
                "color":"yellow",
                "bold": true
            }
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body4",
                "fallback":"抵制不良游戏，拒绝盗版游戏。注意自我保护，谨防受骗上当。适度游戏益脑，沉迷游戏伤身。合理安排时间，享受健康生活。",
                "color":"white"
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body5",
                "fallback":"【快捷操作·小贴士】",
                "color":"yellow",
                "bold": true
            }
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body6",
                "fallback":"· G键：打开「冬战成员用书」",
                "color":"white"
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body7",
                "fallback":"· G键：打开「冬战成员用书」",
                "color":"white"
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body8",
                "fallback":"兵种选择、传送、步话机、百科全书，都在这里。",
                "color":"white"
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body9",
                "fallback":"· 管理员专用：/dialog show @s djzc444:op",
                "color":"white"
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body10",
                "fallback":"只有OP能用的管理面板，可开关Boost、Debug，甚至显示健康忠告。",
                "color":"white"
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body11",
                "fallback":"· 想深入了解？ 资源包和数据包的根目录都附带了一份 README",
                "color":"white"
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body12",
                "fallback":"里面有详细的兵种列表、机制说明、以及一些开发者的碎碎念。",
                "color":"white"
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body13",
                "fallback":"最终用户许可协议（EULA）",
                "color":"yellow",
                "bold": true
            }
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body14",
                "fallback":"1.严禁使用外挂、作弊软件、恶意漏洞。",
                "color":"white",
                "bold": true
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body15",
                "fallback":"无论你在哪个服务器玩冬战，我们都强烈谴责这种行为。公平游戏，是冬战的底线。",
                "color":"white",
                "italic": true
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body14",
                "fallback":"2.你可以自制资源包修改文本、音效、纹理。",
                "color":"white",
                "bold": true
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body15",
                "fallback":"但包里的内容由你负责，与冬战制作组无关。",
                "color":"white",
                "italic": true
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body16",
                "fallback":"3.允许录制视频、直播，或把冬战放进你的整合包并分发。",
                "color":"white",
                "bold": true
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body17",
                "fallback":"需遵守 CC-BY-NC-SA 协议（署名-非商业性-相同方式共享）。",
                "color":"white",
                "italic": true
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body16",
                "fallback":"4.冬战是免费的。",
                "color":"white",
                "bold": true
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body17",
                "fallback":"如果你在任何地方花钱购买了它，你被骗了。",
                "color":"white",
                "italic": true
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body16",
                "fallback":"5.具体服务器的管理规则，请遵守对应服务器的规定。",
                "color":"white",
                "bold": true
            },
            "width": 300
        },
        {
            "type":"plain_message",
            "contents":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula_notice.body17",
                "fallback":"我们管不了每个服，但希望每个服都像60144一样有爱。",
                "color":"white",
                "italic": true
            },
            "width": 300
        }
     ],
     "columns": 2,
     "actions": [
        {
            "label":{
                "translate": "djzc.dialog.eula",
                "fallback": "同意用户协议",
                "color":"gold"
            },
            "action": {
                "type": "run_command",
                "command": "trigger eula set 1"
            }
        }
     ]
}